title = "Welcome to TurretScript!"
initial_position = 2
size = Vector2i(550, 250)
dialog_text = "Welcome to the TurretScript Compiler Demo!

This project demonstrates a fully functional compiler pipeline and Virtual Machine written entirely in GDScript.

1. Write your custom AI script in the IDE (or pick an Example).
2. Click 'Compile' to see your code transform into Tokens, an AST, Symbol Table, and IR Bytecode.
3. Click 'Run' to let the VM execute your bytecode and control the turret.

Enjoy experimenting with the compiler!"
